text: I is a Norwegian heavy metal supergroup. It was formed in 2006 by Abbath Doom Occulta and Armagedda of the band Immortal and TC King of Gorgoroth and Ice Dale of the band Enslaved. Their debut album was Between Two Worlds.It was released on November 3, 2006 in the United Kingdom and November 14, 2006 in North America. == Band members == *Abbath Doom Occulta – vocals, guitar *Ice Dale – guitar *TC King – bass guitar *Armagedda – drums *Demonaz Doom Occulta - lyrics == Discography == ===Albums=== *Between Two Worlds (2006) ==References== == Other websites == *Official website Category:2000s music groups Category:2010s music groups Category:Black metal bands Category:Musical groups established in 2006 Category:Norwegian heavy metal bands Category:Thrash metal bands Category:2006 establishments in Europe
